nf_ingredient_statement: Whole Grain Wheat, Corn Bran, Corn Starch, Inulin, Sugar, Whole Grain Oats, Crisp Oats (Rice Flour, Whole Grain Oats, Sugar, Malt Extract, Salt), Brown Sugar, Corn Syrup, Toasted Oats (Whole Grain Oats, Sugar, Canola Oil, Molasses, Honey), Salt, Honey, Wheat Bits (Whole Grain Wheat, Corn Starch, Com Meal, Sugar, Salt, Trisodium Phosphate, Baking Soda, Color Added), Malt Syrup, Tripotassium Phosphate, Cinnamon, Natural and Artificial Flavor, Sucralose, Color Added. Vitamin E (Mixed Tocopherols) and BHT Added to Preserve Freshness. Vitamins and Minerals: Calcium Carbonate, Zinc And Iron (Mineral Nutrients), Vitamin E (Tocopheryl Acetate), a B Vitamin (Niacinamide), Vitamin C (Sodium Ascorbate), Vitamin B6 (Pyridoxine Hydrochloride), Vitamin B2 (Riboflavin), Vitamin A (Palmitate), Vitamin B1 (Thiamin Mononitrate), a B Vitamin (Folic Acid), Vitamin D3, Vitamin B12.
